flowchart TB
    Q[User query] --> S[Selector LLM, Haiku]
    M[manifest: 1 line per memory file] --> S
    S -->|picks N names| L[Load full memory files]
    L --> P[Inject into next turn's prompt]
    P --> A[Agent LLM, Sonnet]
    A --> R[Answer]

    style S fill:#ffe0b2,stroke:#ef6c00,color:#000
    style A fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32,color:#000
    style M fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
